<li sourcefile="V1/Installation/Install OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA using Docker.md" sourcestartlinenumber="130" sourceendlinenumber="130"><p sourcefile="V1/Installation/Install OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA using Docker.md" sourcestartlinenumber="130" sourceendlinenumber="130">Name the script <em>opcuadockerstart.sh</em> and save it to the directory where you plan to create the container.</p>
</li>
